snippet.title: K/DA x BLACKPINK – More /How You Like That /The Baddest /Ddu-du Ddu-du /Kill This Love MASHUP
snippet.description:
The full title wouldn't fit, so I hope you enjoy this K-Pop mashup of K/DA & Blackpink ft. (G)I-dle, Madison Beer, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine, Bea Miller & Wolftyla. K/DA is too lit. Special shout-out to @1MILLIONDanceStudioofficial for making such a great choreography video with Miyeon and Soyeon. 

Songs used:
Blackpink – Ddu-du Ddu-du (https://youtu.be/IHNzOHi8sJs)
Blackpink – Ddu-du Ddu-du (Remix) (https://youtu.be/u3Y0U1VuJeM)
Blackpink – How You Like That (https://youtu.be/ioNng23DkIM)
Blackpink – Kill This Love (https://youtu.be/2S24-y0Ij3Y)
K/DA – The Baddest (https://youtu.be/RkID8_gnTxw)
K/DA – More (https://youtu.be/3VTkBuxU4yk)
K/DA – Pop/Stars (https://youtu.be/UOxkGD8qRB4)
League of Legends – Take Over (Instrumental) (https://youtu.be/KbNL9ZyB49c)
